HEADWORD: Concatenate
<hw>Con*cat"e*nate</hw> <pr>(k⟦ocr⟧n*k⟦acr⟧t"⟦esl⟧*n⟦amac⟧t)</pr>,
<pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp. & p. p.</pos>
